text: Arben Biba (born 1976 in Pristina, Kosovo) is a Kosovar Albanian actor. He is best known for his role as Alban Krasniqi on the Kosovar soap opera, Stinë Dashurie. ==Filmography== ===Film and Television=== {| class="wikitable sortable" ! Year ! Title !
